For windows, please download sdk from http://theneuromorphic.com

Installation Steps for linux:
1. Copy library into /usr/local/lib
 $ sudo cp lib/linux/libnmengine.so.1 /usr/local/lib

 (MacOS : sudo cp lib/MacOS/libnmengine.1.0.2.dylib /usr/local/lib)

2. Make a link for library
  $ sudo ln -s /usr/local/lib/libnmengine.so.1 /usr/local/lib/libnmengine.so

  (MacOS : sudo ln -s /usr/local/lib/libnmengine.1.0.2.dylib /usr/local/lib/libnmengine.dylib)

3. Support Devices:
  -. Brilliant, Prodigy
